quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,261,METHELUL-LEDHINE JUNFIKUNE ‘EMWALEHUM FI SEBILI ELLAHI KEMETHELI HEBBETIN ‘ENBETET SEB’A SENABILE FI KULLI SUNBULETIN MIA’ETU HEBBETIN WEL-LAHU JUDA’IFU LIMEN JESHA’U WEL-LAHU WASI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  2,262,EL-LEDHINE JUNFIKUNE ‘EMWALEHUM FI SEBILI ELLAHI THUMME LA JUTBI’UNE MA ‘ENFEKU MENNÆN WE LA ‘EDHEN LEHUM ‘EXHRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM WE LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  2,263,KAWLUN MA’RUFUN WE MEGFIRETUN HAJRUN MIN SEDEKATIN JETBA’UHA ‘EDHEN WEL-LAHU GANIJUN HELIMUN
  2,264,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TUBTILU SEDEKATIKUM BIL-MENNI WEL-’EDHA KALLEDHI JUNFIKU MALEHU RI’A’E EN-NASI WE LA JU’UMINU BILLAHI WEL-JEWMIL-’AHIRI FEMETHELUHU KEMETHELI SEFWANIN ‘ALEJHI TURABUN FE’ESABEHU WE EBILUN FETEREKEHU SELDÆN LA JEKDIRUNE ‘ALA S
  2,265,WE METHELUL-LEDHINE JUNFIKUNE ‘EMWALEHUMU EBTIGA’E MERDÆTI ELLAHI WE TETHBITÆN MIN ‘ENFUSIHIM KEMETHELI XHENNETIN BIREBWETIN ‘ESABEHA WE EBILUN FE’ATET ‘UKULEHA DI’FEJNI FE’IN LEM JUSIBHA WE EBILUN FETELLUN WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  2,266,‘EJEWEDDU ‘EHEDUKUM ‘EN TEKUNE LEHU XHENNETUN MIN NEHILIN WE ‘A’NABIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU LEHU FIHA MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI WE ‘ESABEHUL-KIBERU WE LEHU DHURRIJETUN DU’AFA’U FE’ESABEHA ‘I’SARUN FIHI NARUN FAHTEREKAT KEDHALIKE JUBEJJINU ELLAHU LEKUM